      "data": {
        "title": "The Pebble Flow Named To Fast Company’s 2024 List of World Changing Ideas",
        "main_image": {
          "dimensions": { "width": 10027, "height": 5640 },
          "alt": null,
          "copyright": null,
          "url": "https://ik.imagekit.io/dgmbyrekazi/d/ZiKq2vPdc1huKpZ7_PebbleFlow-31.jpg?auto=format,compress",
          "id": "ZiKq2vPdc1huKpZ7",
          "edit": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "zoom": 1, "background": "transparent" }
        },
        "author": "Pebble PR",
        "date": "2024-05-14",
        "slices": [
          {
            "variation": "default",
            "version": "initial",
            "items": [],
            "primary": {
              "content_left": [],
              "content_right": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "RVing should be about enjoying the adventure and the company you keep — not the constant maintenance and concern of the vehicle you are traveling with. Traditional RVs and travel trailers carry burdens like difficult towing, high fuel costs, and a lack of technology. The ongoing upkeep alone can be daunting for any new RVer and a headache for even the most seasoned travelers.",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "That’s why we created the Pebble Flow to change how people go about RVing forever. It’s our response to the long overdue demand for a modern, sustainable, and user-friendly RV. Today, it’s an honor to see our work recognized and Pebble listed as one of Fast Company’s 2024 World Changing Ideas in Transportation.",
                  "spans": [{ "start": 253, "end": 311, "type": "strong" }],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                }
              ],
              "background": "White",
              "separators": false
            },
            "id": "content$e7731938-3f4d-4bb9-b67a-500113951c36",
            "slice_type": "content",
            "slice_label": null
          },
          {
            "variation": "default",
            "version": "initial",
            "items": [
              {
                "image": {
                  "dimensions": { "width": 2501, "height": 1329 },
                  "alt": null,
                  "copyright": null,
                  "url": "https://ik.imagekit.io/dgmbyrekazi/d/ZkOLYiol0Zci9HxC_WCI_Facebook.jpg?auto=format,compress",
                  "id": "ZkOLYiol0Zci9HxC",
                  "edit": {
                    "x": 0,
                    "y": 0,
                    "zoom": 1,
                    "background": "transparent"
                  }
                }
              }
            ],
            "primary": {},
            "id": "slider$5f7cbfd0-2128-4f85-8774-b9690ee1167b",
            "slice_type": "slider",
            "slice_label": null
          },
          {
            "variation": "default",
            "version": "initial",
            "items": [],
            "primary": {
              "content_left": [],
              "content_right": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "This annual awards program focuses on social good, elevating products and concepts that aim to make the world better. The solutions cover everything from renewable energy storage and waste in the fashion industry to a building made entirely from recycled concrete — and we are beyond proud to be listed among such inspiring companies.",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "We’re dedicated to serving those who desire to explore the world on their own terms. As we gear up for production later this year, the Pebble Flow is set to revolutionize how people live, work, and explore — promoting a more sustainable and mobile lifestyle. With impressive early traction and strong community backing, we are ready to lead the transformation of the RV industry into a new, electric age.",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "Looking forward, our hope is that our customers can experience a new lifestyle that allows them to leave behind the things that weigh them down and lead a more sustainable lifestyle with a lighter footprint.",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "Stay tuned for more updates on the Pebble Flow and check out the complete list of Fast Company’s World Changing Ideas:",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "text": "",
                  "spans": [],
                  "direction": "ltr"
                }
              ],
              "background": "White",
              "separators": false
            },
            "id": "content$f9af29c3-2fb1-4bd6-8c5d-6a2e82534c64",
            "slice_type": "content",
            "slice_label": null
          },
